Claude CodeClaude DesktopVS Code / GitHub Copilot Bash<pre><code>claude mcp add -s user --transport sse proxmox http://host.docker.internal:8812/sse
</code></pre> <p>Why <code>host.docker.internal</code>?</p> <p>Claude Code runs inside a Docker container itself, so <code>localhost</code> points to its own container, not your Windows host. <code>host.docker.internal</code> is Docker's bridge to the host machine.</p> <p>Edit <code>C:\Users\&lt;username&gt;\AppData\Roaming\Claude\claude_desktop_config.json</code>:</p> JSON<pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "proxmox": {
      "type": "sse",
      "url": "http://localhost:8812/sse"
    }
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>Restart Claude Desktop to pick up the change.</p> <p>Edit <code>C:\Users\&lt;username&gt;\AppData\Roaming\Code\User\mcp.json</code> and add to the <code>servers</code> object:</p> JSON<pre><code>{
  "servers": {
    "proxmox": {
      "type": "http",
      "url": "http://localhost:8811"
    }
  }
}
</code></pre>
